’t seem right, though. I also ponder if plexus-testing includes a JUnit 5 extension for lookup. I’ll need to check the artifact content!", "thinkingSignature": "{\"id\":\"rs_039c355b798a2e89016a3fc2749cf08195a46575201047d862\",\"type\":\"reasoning\",\"content\":[],\"encrypted_content\":\"gAAAAABqP8J_aczSTMEYIDBEKfCuJ0TGEomPNtO24Jm9SQpdw634I8hv3Gj2MiqQhKnirPy-Di1rXUbFAR95o3Qv7IXSSOlfZ3WdqXK3v3JeAcYBqYBnGf_m5Qhsj5KuSz-iN6ATym1wHe5nQojqeoUDXlEq_l-KXyUk5RScel7jCjwy6k4e11zMRtZkV_BeKMesIXJZqZRBeI1AXMPGULtDuRCTs2xtagzOjHZUOgJA-oIRHeMbcKXnsjLJczsQaEAHePhjycMTOWN7uIdaNXl5MhtFYwkmlhsXXyFdX7ECEKgMjVTtjgL4OP8-cBy_e31A1P00WuBxTdFOgWcRanXm_0jcMiLGOn13BQQap7-vzBF-1aim9Ag8Kk1t9VR-xIXOxgHejqUuQCgGnT_Cc4wWqPtOLxhR1TC08Ewfsztrg-2HvE5kLVaFBP1BCJiEnOrDMI-B_uB4ujlkE-98vnkf-yvmaNapHplregw--o3IHUH8JXRv3-dBJdfdOrfnQ5fw-xsPF8qL47HnBTEQSjeKDZ5cK6SmOKRL-T3fxjqoOchVNE4HVIjZwwSamEDVTSgNsL0Fgk6nuec3LHDGFgay8L0YY1jzZ5-Y4gIeNy0IXU6KOTyAROe7ZlZpFb842atIAx3eDw81k7JWfs-diFH6dXff4yv0t4Yt8nRxI4_b274mqS7fB9j5m5erlEdfECGpTii1jQJ78sfBScPuJ5fko3AKANM0c5uM9BqM2GmrQn3bVsFpklKEXeHdQhs4XKTSGbCYOD9-t6xVHxIatPiU5jzCKPQfdnUnBYdezxReVFrUJhMjzid98QnPmr_Ej0GdLEk32V2JfVdpz21aBl5t8pMzVd0nrxWtRdH89KTc76cknDAKKOHWjMdztNqAqtwC97XtSnbI4zLpgKGAJ5KD7upCjPhgjwd1ei6sfFETCMYc2Qq3Q8W2hHA14o2quzIS7pdghJomAyvW0s38ZngmulAj_qjIfTukb8ADsD39Q90q5KUniw_M6St40giiOHAMzDyZHh4tNZfLunZH9SXi224QKrH2fMHE9UXCTUD9I8PfW_wWGKjUW3tRC5ITxxJUImgGKC7HVcZ-lNT8i8vHZPFjT4egm11aeTDONvYAuYpxpoJGuY86ZCJ6Mf1MtmTUfzBlewPzuXiFCC-VEr8asS-3eueF-LBqUwlVwwPKQfw9mC3RvBqgx7KWGP287P8ld9TztlGxvOdJ_-26TkneXLaAXHHpqVef_8gpk3CY5Ij2CqAKH-P6LX7DUcBWRTkeqX4RwOrZaviul0adBVLZ6qD6xyBfmyfWkCiLM2jC3SX9PpiSJC0GYX8dPK5qXMBEYfX_ciIQhtVw4uamri3LVHmNfviK6zQHactcHBvxswwDiHao0HpD-6sUf0z7Eczh7wVQbDl0xKDndfMMWI2UPkaSH5l_YTVUC3kQgofqHBTW650e84iP3oujKeRfT9WkulIPzI1x3MjrGJ3KxeS-qLF5fqIF7CAadcbGZHX-23sRGM-8FLBEDtwpK_N-6A-77j48J67dXX7GGK21UQofd_WqDN_jll62pGttfUcP3YjZy6w4ZYp3dpr2um17c169a69baHNoXbm8o8oWMllvcMR_Io9XdDpfRyY8CCVIDBCF6YV-ITdMAWG2LW7YD3e8Z9E9h4ruryecmlm4OnF-_HWxkm_8CP9V38dxLu_Yvrk